'''''Seasons of a Life,''''' ni filimi yasohotse 2010 nka Malawi Legal drama film iyoborwa na  Shemu Joyah na vyahinguwe n'Ivyabona FirstDawn Arts.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Bennie Msuku ayoboye hamwe na Neria Chikhosi, Flora Suya na Tapiwa Gwaza bagize uruhare runini.  

Ikinamico yemewe ninkiko yibanze kumukozi wo murugo wasambanijwe numukoresha we uharanira kwiha ku imbaraga no kuzamura imibereho ye.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Göteborg muri [[Suwede]] ku ya 31 Mutarama 2010. Iyi filime kandi yatorewe ibihembo mu birori bya [[Kenya]], Cairo, na Zanzibar.  Yatowe mu byiciro 8 mu bihembo bya 6 bya African Movie Academy Awards, harimo abahatanira ibihembo byiza byerekana amashusho meza hamwe n’umwimerere mwiza. Umukinnyi wa filime, Tapiwa Gwaza yatsindiye igihembo cya Nollywood kubera ibikorwa byiza byakozwe numukinnyi ushyigikiwe.

